author: Jim VandeHei
title: The next American struggle: Waiting out the coronavirus
description: There are now a lot of known knowns about the coronavirus: It's here, it's spreading, it's stressing hospitals, it's crippling the economy, it's slowed only by distance and isolation — and it's sure to get much worse before it gets much better. Why it matters…
